{"tid":481483,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"世上兩大ON9收費 醫院巡房費 考車租車費","createTime":"2017-11-27T08:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T16:34:10.000Z","uid":68626,"like":75,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"51278f44e95982c748bbe4a49d8326daefba5b50","tid":481483,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"巡房費 屌你老母 問你兩句野 有冇唔舒服<br />\n多謝幾百蚊 仆你個街<br />\n做完手術 確認個病人有冇頭暈唔舒服係你責任黎<br />\n就拎左黎收錢<br />\n<br />\n考車租車費 依加已經多謝1800大元<br />\n屌那星<br />\n平時學車個陣就唔撚洗租車錢既<br />\n到左考試個陣無啦啦比1800蚊你完全唔知做乜鳩<br />\nR你架車用15分鐘 1800蚊 仲貴撚過總統套房<br />\n完全不明所以<br />\n<br />\n如果市民繼續比呢兩樣收費存在<br />\n黎緊可能就會出現 銀行開戶口:查詢費 連登開AC:開戶費 砌機:租場費(砌機唔洗地方)"},{"pid":"19202b00e313c60fd7ed9f57a144ac4e6319ab8f","tid":481483,"uid":52611,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T08:37:44.000Z","msg":"考車肥佬都可以哭喪甘耐 廢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d94bd3da259a031fcd7b1ed58b32d5a7bb7e472","tid":481483,"uid":3643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"租車貴在保險？"},{"pid":"fd9b014cb3c2fa76232135d664f0c0ace1996962","tid":481483,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"租車費好似係保險費？"},{"pid":"0e3bc4b2a6d56dee1d4d56c9bc8cda2db8c9d944","tid":481483,"uid":6032,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租車費好似係保險費？</blockquote><br />\n根本班仆街合謀定價<br />\n上堂又呃鐘<br />\n未落堂就叫你揸定去第二度<br />\n考試租車千幾蚊再加鐘錢2千幾 林寶都租到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07730ed8da2eaf040a16c5e9b3737d2b8d86c27","tid":481483,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a6b3323ea17d7